# Python AI Service

- FastAPI with health/ready endpoints; structured logging with PII redaction.
- No direct connection to business PostgreSQL tables.
- All business mutations go through typed tool calls to the NestJS API with authorization.
- No production prompt/model activation without eval, approval, rollback, and kill switch.
- Timeouts and cancellation on all external/model calls.
- Redact raw prompts, provider tokens, and full request bodies from logs.
